dct_title_s: Map of the East Fork of Little Miami River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. East Fork of Little Miami River Basin
dct_description_sm: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water
Scale bar lower center of map.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the East Fork of the Little Miami River Basin and quality of underground water.
